<L>__{interior saucier municipal building day}
<A>__{the sheriff is busy on the phone; there is a deputy today also on the phone. the sheriff, seeing mrs. munson enter, covers the phone with one hand.}
<C>__{sheriff wyner}
<D>__{miz munson.}
